text: Michel Grall (born September 11, 1961 in Carnac) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Morbihan department, and is a member of the Union for a Popular Movement. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:People from Carnac Category:Union for a Popular Movement politicians Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
title: Michel Grall
